                <h2><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Introduction</h2>
                <p>This personal website is created and maintained by me (Maroof Lone). All writings, photos, projects and/or any other material on this site are original unless clearly stated otherwise. I believe in transparency and respect for user privacy.</p>
