                <p>I handle digital safety and user privacy with the utmost care. This website utilizes secure, encrypted connections (HTTPS) and is hosted on secure servers to protect your browsing experience. While I take robust measures to protect any data you submit via contact forms, please remember that no transmission over the internet is completely infallible. Please do not send highly sensitive personal information through public contact channels.</p>
