            <section class="privacy-section">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-history"></i> Information Retention</h2>
                <p>If you reach out to me via email or a contact form, I will keep our correspondence only as long as necessary to fulfill your request or answer your inquiry. I routinely clean out old communication data and do not maintain a permanent database of visitor contact information.</p>
